{"tid":742824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍北乏娛樂設施　多街童","createTime":"2018-07-15T01:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T08:19:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"557a1df2c31d44e2ce687862c0ffae8ae02446ae","tid":742824,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180715/20450279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180715%2F20450279&d=3Y7Se3kkqDpUS4pkafFwLpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=fed3d33d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180715%2F20450279&h=ded5defe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180715/20450279</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月15日 <br />\n<br />\n天水圍北乏娛樂設施　多街童<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180715/large/17687206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180715%2Flarge%2F17687206.jpg&h=d9c71d39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■元朗區議員李月民指，今次事件疑兇近乎以「家法」方式教訓對方，超出一般欺凌範圍。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天水圍發生令人震驚的女童遭凌虐事件，有區議員指天水圍北2000年後湧入大量新生家庭，父母要出外搵食導致疏於管教，區內缺乏娛樂設施，又不夠社工資源疏理青少年問題，造成近年童黨問題惡化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社工外展服務嚴重不足<br />\n<br />\n本身是註冊社工的元朗區議員李月民指，天水圍分南北兩邊發展，南邊如嘉湖山莊早於1992年起步，當時有大批家庭遷入，當年的孩童大部份已投入社會工作，反而天水圍北如天恆邨及天澤邨至2000年才開始發展，當時有大量新生家庭湧入，家長要出外搵食導致疏於管教，加上當區社會資源貧乏，大批街童無所事事成為黑幫吸納對象，逐步浮現童黨問題。李認為今次事件近乎以「家法」方式教訓對方，超出一般欺凌範圍，當局須正視。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員兼元朗區議員鄺俊宇表示，該區最大的青少年問題是社工外展服務嚴重不足，近年甚至出現隱性童黨個案，例如雙方在通訊群組內起哄，再「吹雞」相約出外講數，至揭發事件時雙方已大打出手，社工難以在事件萌芽時阻止，促政府增撥社工資源，先從校園開始遏止童黨問題。<br />\n<br />\n■記者莫家文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n網民稱15歲主腦吸毒愛打人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n秀茂坪童黨燒屍　4人囚終身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民稱15歲主腦吸毒愛打人<br />\n<br />\n秀茂坪童黨燒屍　4人囚終身<br />\n<br />\n脫光掌摑　火燒陰毛　棍襲下體14歲女遭童黨凌虐留醫"},{"pid":"82aa0e3b9278a9e5a2ea727cb0cb328b1e768981","tid":742824,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750308474299e4bd3011b5a501b30698b6102ded","tid":742824,"uid":58335,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"關咩事呀<br />\n<br />\n個邊D人係低等D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fec0d6a3061a5ef9fbe1029d62d04c494a45a23","tid":742824,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:38:17.000Z","msg":"應該要賴八萬五建屋目標 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c8648e81aafc68bad21ae43cde3854a0cd4241","tid":742824,"uid":54733,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"多娛樂設施唔係會更多mk聚集咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7873f71ba33f7acab7f39d2c13c31f6bfdb4fed8","tid":742824,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:39:17.000Z","msg":"d街童無野玩咪拎人地條命黎玩囉<br />\n上面又話150無問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基建都未起好就放咁撚多人落黎"},{"pid":"a51cea3b403b5bc77307e84d3f24b802589dfc1a","tid":742824,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"天水圍樓爆？"},{"pid":"2d882e0f8eb69db607673ddf0b8983f7dd3d2994","tid":742824,"uid":53922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係咪要區議會批十億比你起娛樂設施？<br />\n直接D講，OK? 唔夠錢洗咪講囉。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b88a4bf2dd8f95c8a15366bf99a6ede67d68bc","tid":742824,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"